13
00:00:52,202 --> 00:00:55,005
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu akan membuatmu terdengar
seperti orang gila. Jadi...</font>

14
00:00:55,005 --> 00:00:56,039
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak.</font>

15
00:00:59,810 --> 00:01:01,778
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku harus memberitahu
dia kebenarannya.</font>

16
00:01:08,685 --> 00:01:09,786
<font color=#FFFF00>Disini...</font>

17
00:01:12,689 --> 00:01:14,825
<font color=#FFFF00>...ada orang lain
yang sedang bersama kita.</font>

18
00:01:16,693 --> 00:01:18,228
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau mungkin berpikir aku gila,</font>

19
00:01:18,695 --> 00:01:19,996
<font color=#FFFF00>...tapi aku tidak...</font>

20
00:01:22,566 --> 00:01:24,468
<font color=#FFFF00>...ingin menyembunyikan ini darimu lagi.
Bahkan jika kau tidak percaya,</font>

21
00:01:28,472 --> 00:01:30,407
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku ingin mengatakan
yang sebenarnya.</font>

22
00:01:31,074 --> 00:01:33,043
<font color=#FFFF00>Jadi maksudmu...</font>

23
00:01:34,077 --> 00:01:37,214
<font color=#FFFF00>Ada orang lain di sini
selain kita berdua, begitu?</font>

24
00:01:37,414 --> 00:01:39,649
<font color=#FFFF00>Roh penipu yang
keluar dari tubuhnya.</font>

25
00:01:40,717 --> 00:01:42,853
<font color=#FFFF00>Astaga, ini tidak baik.</font>

26
00:01:42,986 --> 00:01:44,855
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia tampak terkejut.</font>

27
00:01:45,355 --> 00:01:48,525
<font color=#FFFF00>Hentikan sampai disini saja.</font>

28
00:01:48,525 --> 00:01:50,060
<font color=#FFFF00>Dan roh itu...</font>

29
00:01:53,897 --> 00:01:55,465
<font color=#FFFF00>...merasuki tubuhku.</font>

30
00:02:05,742 --> 00:02:07,377
<font color=#FFFF00>Jadi maksudmu...</font>

31
00:02:07,577 --> 00:02:12,182
<font color=#FFFF00>...kau dirasuki oleh roh penipu?</font>

32
00:02:12,749 --> 00:02:14,518
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau ingin aku percaya?</font>

33
00:02:28,098 --> 00:02:29,533
<font color=#FFFF00>Seperti apa wajahnya?</font>

34
00:02:33,236 --> 00:02:34,404
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa ini benar?</font>

35
00:02:40,143 --> 00:02:41,144
<font color=#FFFF00>Iya.</font>

36
00:02:42,646 --> 00:02:43,880
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu benar.</font>

37
00:02:47,918 --> 00:02:49,452
<font color=#FFFF00>Anggap saja kau benar,</font>

38
00:02:50,053 --> 00:02:52,889
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan roh penipu itu benar ada.</font>

39
00:02:54,291 --> 00:02:56,393
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa namanya...</font>

40
00:02:58,261 --> 00:02:59,863
<font color=#FFFF00>...Gong Soo Chang?</font>

41
00:03:01,097 --> 00:03:02,299
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya, Ssong.</font>

42
00:03:03,200 --> 00:03:04,534
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini aku, Gong Soo Chang.</font>

43
00:03:08,939 --> 00:03:10,607
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu benar dia.</font>

44
00:03:12,409 --> 00:03:13,643
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak masuk akal.</font>

45
00:03:15,245 --> 00:03:18,081
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak bermaksud menyembunyikan
ini dari.../ Berhenti.</font>

46
00:03:18,381 --> 00:03:21,685
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku sangat bingung sampai
tidak bisa bicara apa-apa.</font>

47
00:03:23,954 --> 00:03:25,188
<font color=#FFFF00>Kita bahas nanti saja.</font>

48
00:05:18,068 --> 00:05:20,437
<font color=#FFFF00>DUA POLISI</font>

49
00:06:32,575 --> 00:06:33,710
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa Ssong...</font>

50
00:06:34,511 --> 00:06:35,645
<font color=#FFFF00>...baik-baik saja?</font>

51
00:06:38,815 --> 00:06:40,116
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia akan baik-baik saja.</font>

52
00:06:42,752 --> 00:06:44,120
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia tampaknya sangat terkejut.</font>

53
00:06:44,120 --> 00:06:46,256
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia pasti bisa menerimanya.
Aku percaya padanya.</font>

54
00:06:49,459 --> 00:06:53,129
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia selalu berani tanpa berpikir
