113
00:09:51,874 --> 00:09:53,142
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku pergi.</font>

114
00:09:57,747 --> 00:09:59,515
<font color=#FFFF00><i>[Gong Soo Chang, Cha Dong Tak, harus menyelesaikan
